name: Edition 2/22 tarot card - The Magician
description:
Size: 2362 x 4725 px
This edition card will be released every 4 days.

Let's unleash the magic power within you! You already have all the abilities to achieve your goals. Now is the time to concentrate and focus because The Magician will support you. She is a really good friend and very confident with her power.

She appears to be playing with cups (her magic tools) to change your idea into reality. She also has a wand, which represents desire and inspiration. The infinity sign shows her unlimited potential to always help you. Her magic looks like red roses, which shows emotion and passion.

The Magician is numbered 1 in the Major Arcana cards, bringing together the world and the spiritual as well as conduit converting physical energy into real-world action.

*This item is available only as a Non-Fungible Token (NFT). It’s strictly prohibited to steal and reduplicate this NFT item.
